2231
01:12:49,399 --> 01:12:51,298
- We avoided a big issue.
- We avoided a big issue.

2232
01:12:51,299 --> 01:12:53,639
- Right.
- We would've been in big trouble.

2233
01:12:54,039 --> 01:12:56,909
It's great to talk like this.

2234
01:12:57,869 --> 01:12:59,169
Well,

2235
01:13:00,739 --> 01:13:02,308
I feel grateful to be able...

2236
01:13:02,309 --> 01:13:04,049
- to spend flashy moments, - Right.

2237
01:13:04,179 --> 01:13:07,449
