2250
01:13:30,709 --> 01:13:34,108
Yunho has tried all sorts of things on our show today.

2251
01:13:34,109 --> 01:13:35,578
I'm experiencing everything I can.

2252
01:13:35,579 --> 01:13:37,478
- He went into the water.
- Right.

2253
01:13:37,479 --> 01:13:39,348
