- Right.

2254
01:13:39,349 --> 01:13:40,749
He had rice and kimchi.

2255
01:13:41,279 --> 01:13:43,689
I'll remember that kimchi for a long time.

2256
01:13:44,289 --> 01:13:45,818
Sleep well.

2257
01:13:45,819 --> 01:13:47,088
- Sleep well.
- Let's cheer up.

2258
01:13:47,089 --> 01:13:48,358
- Right.
- Have good dreams.

2259
01:13:48,359 --> 01:13:50,228
- Great work today.
- Great work.

2260
01:13:50,229 --> 01:13:51,289
Great work.

2261
