(Snoring)

2262
01:13:54,929 --> 01:13:58,829
(The human drill gets to work all of a sudden.)

2263
01:13:59,999 --> 01:14:02,499
(His snoring really is irregular!)

2264
01:14:03,109 --> 01:14:05,469
(Joon manages to block the noise completely with an item.)

2265
01:14:05,739 --> 01:14:06,809
(Snoring)

2266
01:14:07,309 --> 01:14:09,309
(With Jae Jun's passionate snoring, )

2267
01:14:10,249 --> 01:14:13,349
(the passionate day goes by.)

2268
01:14:14,349 --> 01:14:16,549
