2269
01:14:17,549 --> 01:14:21,089
(It's early in the morning while it's still foggy.)

2270
01:14:26,399 --> 01:14:29,399
(Yunho gets up 1 hour before the wake-up song.)

2271
01:14:29,799 --> 01:14:32,198
