2274
01:14:37,569 --> 01:14:39,039
Yunho is up already?

2275
01:14:40,279 --> 01:14:42,139
The lenses are foggy.

2276
01:14:42,579 --> 01:14:45,179
(Why did Yunho get up early?)

2277
01:14:45,249 --> 01:14:46,519
- Where are you going?
- Well,

2278
01:14:47,119 --> 01:14:49,718
I have morning aerobic workouts in an empty stomach.

2279
01:14:49,719 --> 01:14:51,749
(Aerobic workouts in an empty stomach?)

2280
01:14:51,819 --> 01:14:53,565
Morning aerobic workouts in an empty stomach?

2281
01:14:53,589 --> 01:15:00,759
(His morning aerobic workout in an empty stomach begins.)

2282
01:15:01,759 --> 01:15:04,268
(Like a deity that rises in the East, )

2283
01:15:04,269 --> 01:15:07,039
(his passion awakens.)

2284
01:15:07,599 --> 01:15:10,739
(His passion burns bright.)

2285
01:15:11,209 --> 01:15:12,239
(Breathing out)

2286
01:15:12,839 --> 01:15:14,909
(He runs out of breath)

2287
01:15:15,609 --> 01:15:18,549
("I, U-Know Yunho, will keep running.")

2288
01:15:19,379 --> 01:15:21,649
I must live well today...

2289
01:15:21,779 --> 01:15:23,299
to be able to choose to live tomorrow.

2290
01:15:23,989 --> 01:15:25,348
(After 30 minutes of his aerobic workout)

2291
01:15:25,349 --> 01:15:27,089
All right! Let's wake up!

2292
01:15:28,189 --> 01:15:29,689
Let's wake up!

2293
01:15:30,459 --> 01:15:31,929
Let's wake up!

2294
01:15:32,429 --> 01:15:34,359
- The wake-up song didn't go off.
- Gosh.

2295
01:15:35,099 --> 01:15:36,259
All right!

2296
01:15:36,629 --> 01:15:38,498
I'm the wake-up song.

2297
01:15:38,499 --> 01:15:39,699
- Gosh!
- Gosh!

2298
01:15:39,899 --> 01:15:41,238
(DinDin wakes up thanks to the human wake-up song.)

2299
01:15:41,239 --> 01:15:43,539
- Gosh!
- One, two, three!

2300
01:15:44,109 --> 01:15:45,838
(Jong Min literally gets forced to get up.)

2301
01:15:45,839 --> 01:15:47,309
Oh, gosh. I was forced to get up.

2302
01:15:47,909 --> 01:15:49,108
Right.

2303
01:15:49,109 --> 01:15:50,785
(The members of Team Sleep Outdoors are all up.)

2304
01:15:50,809 --> 01:15:51,809
All right!

2305
01:15:52,609 --> 01:15:54,149
It's time to wake up!

2306
01:15:54,849 --> 01:15:56,948
(He gets up at the sound of Yunho's voice.)

2307
01:15:56,949 --> 01:15:58,119
Turn the lights on!

2308
01:15:58,289 --> 01:16:00,258
- All right.
- Gosh.

2309
01:16:00,259 --> 01:16:02,518
(Yunho hesitates to go in.)

2310
01:16:02,519 --> 01:16:05,388
I want to go in, but it feels like I shouldn't go in.

2311
01:16:05,389 --> 01:16:06,599
- It's fine.
- Okay.

2312
01:16:08,359 --> 01:16:09,869
Come out with passion!

2313
01:16:10,699 --> 01:16:12,699
Hurry up and get out!

2314
01:16:13,599 --> 01:16:14,869
Go!

2315
01:16:15,469 --> 01:16:18,409
- You have to get dressed.
- Right.

2316
01:16:18,909 --> 01:16:20,509
Be passionate in the morning.

2317
01:16:20,609 --> 01:16:24,479
(He wakes up passionately while being half-naked.)

2318
01:16:24,679 --> 01:16:26,918
- Did you have a good night's sleep?
- Yes.

2319
01:16:26,919 --> 01:16:28,525
(All members wake up quickly thanks to Yunho.)

2320
01:16:28,549 --> 01:16:30,989
If I ever come to 2 Days 1 Night again,

2321
01:16:31,089 --> 01:16:32,819
I should do vocal exercises.

2322
01:16:33,059 --> 01:16:34,899
- I lost my voice.
- You lose your voice here.

2323
01:16:35,359 --> 01:16:39,759
(They did this chant for 20 times yesterday.)

2324
01:16:40,829 --> 01:16:42,999
(His throat couldn't handle his passion.)

2325
01:16:43,029 --> 01:16:45,428
You all look much closer than yesterday.

2326
01:16:45,429 --> 01:16:46,438
Right.

2327
01:16:46,439 --> 01:16:47,798
Do you feel at ease now?

2328
01:16:47,799 --> 01:16:51,169
- Joon and I are like brothers now.
- Really?

2329
01:16:51,439 --> 01:16:53,008
Fortunately, he said I didn't snore.

2330
01:16:53,009 --> 01:16:54,038
- Right.
- Really?

2331
01:16:54,039 --> 01:16:55,408
He did snore.

2332
01:16:55,409 --> 01:16:56,848
- But it was weaker than I thought.
- Really?

2333
01:16:56,849 --> 01:16:59,149
- You should feel ashamed.
- Why is that?

2334
01:16:59,249 --> 01:17:01,378
He said it wasn't that strong after all that I said.

2335
01:17:01,379 --> 01:17:03,448
- You should've shown him.
- He got nervous.

2336
01:17:03,449 --> 01:17:05,148
- He got too nervous to perform.
- It was weaker than I thought.

2337
01:17:05,149 --> 01:17:06,818
Joon is looking down on you.

2338
01:17:06,819 --> 01:17:08,158
- He says I'm stronger than you.
- It was disappointing.

2339
01:17:08,159 --> 01:17:10,859
Let's spend the night together again somewhere else.

2340
01:17:10,929 --> 01:17:12,058
That's fine.

2341
01:17:12,059 --> 01:17:13,829
Show him what you've got at your place.

2342
01:17:13,959 --> 01:17:16,729
(Joon just missed it. It was strong enough.)

2343
01:17:16,869 --> 01:17:18,999
We'll start with the morning mission right away.

2344
01:17:19,229 --> 01:17:21,838
- If you look over there...
- There are numbers for the rooms.

2345
01:17:21,839 --> 01:17:24,838
You see the room numbers from 1 to 6, right?

2346
01:17:24,839 --> 01:17:28,238
Each person will choose a room to enter.

2347
01:17:28,239 --> 01:17:29,949
From 1 to 6, all in separate rooms?

2348
01:17:30,049 --> 01:17:31,555
Right. Each of you will choose a room.

2349
01:17:31,579 --> 01:17:34,118
Will things get decided as soon as we enter a room?

2350
01:17:34,119 --> 01:17:36,218
You'll be told what to do once you enter.

2351
01:17:36,219 --> 01:17:37,949
Is this not part of the game?

2352
01:17:38,189 --> 01:17:40,358
- No.
- It won't matter right now?

2353
01:17:40,359 --> 01:17:42,488
Okay. Let's go. Let's see what happens.

2354
01:17:42,489 --> 01:17:43,989
Okay! See you later.

2355
01:17:44,659 --> 01:17:47,258
I feel like I've gotten closer to Se Yoon.

2356
01:17:47,259 --> 01:17:49,529
- Really?
- Se Yoon farted while sleeping.

2357
01:17:50,529 --> 01:17:51,568
I showed you everything.

2358
01:17:51,569 --> 01:17:55,639
(They share their farts after just a single night together.)

2359
01:17:55,739 --> 01:17:58,308
I wish to see ramyeon as soon as I enter.

2360
01:17:58,309 --> 01:17:59,545
(Jae Jun wishes to see ramyeon.)

2361
01:17:59,569 --> 01:18:00,638
Is this right?

2362
01:18:00,639 --> 01:18:03,378
(What is the morning mission for the separated members?)

2363
01:18:03,379 --> 01:18:04,879
- What is this?
- Gosh.

2364
01:18:05,549 --> 01:18:07,148
Start by taking this pen.

2365
01:18:07,149 --> 01:18:08,579
- The pen?
- Yes.

2366
01:18:09,279 --> 01:18:10,449
From now on...

2367
01:18:11,119 --> 01:18:13,079
Choose the one you feel you got the closest to...

2368
01:18:13,159 --> 01:18:15,589
- through this trip.
- Through this trip.

2369
01:18:16,389 --> 01:18:18,188
Write that person's name on your palm.

2370
01:18:18,189 --> 01:18:19,529
My palm?

2371
01:18:21,299 --> 01:18:23,629
The one I got closest to?

2372
01:18:24,069 --> 01:18:27,338
I got really close to Yunho while farting in my sleep.

2373
01:18:27,339 --> 01:18:29,069
"We got a lot closer, Se Yoon."

2374
01:18:29,369 --> 01:18:31,938
"I heard your farting and snoring."

2375
01:18:31,939 --> 01:18:34,109
He mentioned this just now. What do I do?

2376
01:18:34,379 --> 01:18:36,209
We weren't close at all.

2377
01:18:36,409 --> 01:18:38,809
It was nice talking to him.

2378
01:18:38,879 --> 01:18:40,618
He was passionate...

2379
01:18:40,619 --> 01:18:43,049
during the games. And...

2380
01:18:44,189 --> 01:18:46,988
I'm torn between two people.

2381
01:18:46,989 --> 01:18:48,709
(Popular Yunho is torn between two people.)

2382
01:18:50,129 --> 01:18:54,059
It seems like we got close naturally.

2383
01:18:55,659 --> 01:18:57,228
Since we have to win...

2384
01:18:57,229 --> 01:18:59,699
(Joon chooses someone to win the game.)

2385
01:19:00,569 --> 01:19:01,698
(All of them wrote the names.)

2386
01:19:01,699 --> 01:19:02,969
This ink is removable, right?

2387
01:19:03,809 --> 01:19:05,969
The morning mission will begin now.

2388
01:19:06,309 --> 01:19:07,978
It's Love Line.

2389
01:19:07,979 --> 01:19:09,439
- What?
- Love Line?

2390
01:19:09,479 --> 01:19:11,448
- When there's a match, - I don't think I'll find a match.

2391
01:19:11,449 --> 01:19:12,578
Will the two go on a date?

2392
01:19:12,579 --> 01:19:15,099
- Isn't it bad to find a match?
- Isn't it bad to find a match?

2393
01:19:15,149 --> 01:19:16,518
Joon will go first.

2394
01:19:16,519 --> 01:19:17,619
- What?
- What?

2395
01:19:17,949 --> 01:19:20,018
Joon, show us your choice.

2396
01:19:20,019 --> 01:19:22,318
- With this...
- You end up getting attached.

2397
01:19:22,319 --> 01:19:24,159
Who did he like?

2398
01:19:24,289 --> 01:19:26,288
- Kang Jae Jun.
- Kang Jae Jun.

2399
01:19:26,289 --> 01:19:27,859
- He's...
- Why did you choose him?

2400
01:19:28,229 --> 01:19:29,229
We slept together.

2401
01:19:29,329 --> 01:19:30,628
- You slept together.
- In the same room?

2402
01:19:30,629 --> 01:19:31,698
Yes.

2403
01:19:31,699 --> 01:19:33,468
He took his clothes off and slept next to me.

2404
01:19:33,469 --> 01:19:35,168
And the reason I grew even more fond of him...

2405
01:19:35,169 --> 01:19:37,239
is that he slept looking in my direction.

2406
01:19:37,509 --> 01:19:38,789
- Without his clothes on?
- Yes.

2407
01:19:39,109 --> 01:19:41,378
On 2 Days 1 Night, you grow attached to each other while sleeping.

2408
01:19:41,379 --> 01:19:42,738
- Right.
- That's true.

2409
01:19:42,739 --> 01:19:44,308
We become closer while sleeping together.

2410
01:19:44,309 --> 01:19:47,419
I think it had a significant impact.

2411
01:19:47,579 --> 01:19:49,779
DinDin, show us your choice.

2412
01:19:50,749 --> 01:19:52,719
Yunho of TVXQ.

2413
01:19:53,419 --> 01:19:54,658
You were already close.

2414
01:19:54,659 --> 01:19:55,888
- How could you become even closer?
- Right.

2415
01:19:55,889 --> 01:19:59,188
I've known him for ten years.

2416
01:19:59,189 --> 01:20:01,359
I liked that he looked...

2417
01:20:01,859 --> 01:20:03,629
exactly the same now...

2418
01:20:04,169 --> 01:20:06,969
as he did when we worked together ten years ago.

2419
01:20:08,069 --> 01:20:11,169
(With Yunho, who is still just as passionate, )

2420
01:20:12,109 --> 01:20:15,079
(he played games for 2 days and 1 night, )

2421
01:20:15,979 --> 01:20:18,049
(and he felt even closer to him.)

2422
01:20:18,949 --> 01:20:21,649
(So, DinDin's choice is Yunho.)

2423
01:20:21,779 --> 01:20:25,219
I also grew fond of him while sleeping together. So...

2424
01:20:28,219 --> 01:20:29,258
Who? Joon?

2425
01:20:29,259 --> 01:20:30,959
Se Yoon, I thought we were close already.

2426
01:20:31,629 --> 01:20:33,728
I wanted to take care of my friend, so I chose Jae Jun.

2427
01:20:33,729 --> 01:20:35,028
What? I thought...

2428
01:20:35,029 --> 01:20:36,629
(Se Yoon chose his old friend, Jae Jun.)

2429
01:20:37,169 --> 01:20:39,098
I guess I'm popular.

2430
01:20:39,099 --> 01:20:40,338
Thanks.

2431
01:20:40,339 --> 01:20:43,609
(Se Yoon chose his long-lasting friendship.)

2432
01:20:43,739 --> 01:20:45,408
Now, Jong Min,

2433
01:20:45,409 --> 01:20:46,708
- Yes.
- show us your choice.

2434
01:20:46,709 --> 01:20:49,708
I watched his very first TV show.

2435
01:20:49,709 --> 01:20:52,249
I know what he was like when he first debuted.

2436
01:20:52,979 --> 01:20:54,948
I've watched him ever since.

2437
01:20:54,949 --> 01:20:57,788
I still remember that TVXQ...

2438
01:20:57,789 --> 01:20:59,388
You said that already.

2439
01:20:59,389 --> 01:21:00,858
You revealed your choice.

2440
01:21:00,859 --> 01:21:02,718
- Go away.
- I can't believe this.

2441
01:21:02,719 --> 01:21:03,889
- Why?
- I thought it was me.

2442
01:21:04,459 --> 01:21:06,019
We only exchanged greetings in passing,

2443
01:21:06,589 --> 01:21:08,105
and he sang a congratulatory song at my wedding.

2444
01:21:08,129 --> 01:21:10,569
However, we never spent a long time together before.

2445
01:21:11,629 --> 01:21:13,368
(Jong Min's choice is Yunho.)

2446
01:21:13,369 --> 01:21:15,238
- It's a tie.
- It's two and two.

2447
01:21:15,239 --> 01:21:17,439
- Two and two.
- Now we have two people left.

2448
01:21:17,739 --> 01:21:19,869
Everyone, if your choices match,

2449
01:21:21,009 --> 01:21:22,038
you'll get off work.

2450
01:21:22,039 --> 01:21:24,048
(They get off right away.)

2451
01:21:24,049 --> 01:21:25,108
If our choices match?

2452
01:21:25,109 --> 01:21:26,448
I see. But...

2453
01:21:26,449 --> 01:21:29,878
Hang on. I think I'll be very disappointed.

2454
01:21:29,879 --> 01:21:33,149
I think we might end up cutting ties with each other today.

2455
01:21:33,219 --> 01:21:35,719
If our choices didn't match, would we want to cry?

2456
01:21:36,189 --> 01:21:37,909
Because I have a lot of memories like that.

2457
01:21:39,459 --> 01:21:41,298
When I hung out with other clubs,

2458
01:21:41,299 --> 01:21:42,829
I would end up alone.

2459
01:21:43,399 --> 01:21:45,929
We will talk about it later.

2460
01:21:46,399 --> 01:21:47,538
I'm nervous.

2461
01:21:47,539 --> 01:21:49,199
And now,

2462
01:21:49,839 --> 01:21:52,008
we will first find out...

2463
01:21:52,009 --> 01:21:53,778
- Jae Jun's choice.
- This is driving me crazy.

2464
01:21:53,779 --> 01:21:56,109
It should be either Lee Joon or Moon Se Yoon.

2465
01:21:56,439 --> 01:21:58,878
- I feel so bad.
- What if he chose someone else?

2466
01:21:58,879 --> 01:22:00,148
If he chose someone...

2467
01:22:00,149 --> 01:22:01,618
like Jong Min, it would be interesting.

2468
01:22:01,619 --> 01:22:03,178
To be honest, I wanted to pick U-Know Yunho.

2469
01:22:03,179 --> 01:22:04,448
He was my first choice.

2470
01:22:04,449 --> 01:22:06,318
I was just being nice to you because you're my friend.

2471
01:22:06,319 --> 01:22:07,788
Then, you should change it now.

2472
01:22:07,789 --> 01:22:09,389
I can't because it's a permanent marker.

2473
01:22:09,589 --> 01:22:12,129
- They got us a permanent marker.
- Right. They did.

2474
01:22:12,289 --> 01:22:14,499
I have to shoot another show tomorrow, and...

2475
01:22:14,999 --> 01:22:16,275
- Seriously...
- It says Jae Jun.

2476
01:22:16,299 --> 01:22:17,868
And it's Dr. Oh Eun Yeong's show.

