Of course, he can.

2595
01:26:22,039 --> 01:26:23,278
Think about it.

2596
01:26:23,279 --> 01:26:24,748
Your passion and spirit of challenge.

2597
01:26:24,749 --> 01:26:26,048
You even went into the water with us.

2598
01:26:26,049 --> 01:26:27,118
The mountain is treacherous.

2599
