He even got into the water yesterday. Right?

2608
01:26:44,929 --> 01:26:48,299
(Once I make up my mind, I just stick to it.)

2609
01:26:49,139 --> 01:26:50,169
Let's go!

2610
01:26:51,109 --> 01:26:52,369
