2615
01:27:01,679 --> 01:27:04,388
DinDin will go home, and I'll stay to finish it off.

2616
01:27:04,389 --> 01:27:06,288
The cameraman in charge of you...

2617
01:27:06,289 --> 01:27:07,789
can't even go home.

2618
01:27:08,189 --> 01:27:09,889
All right.

2619
01:27:10,559 --> 01:27:11,758
Passion!

2620
01:27:11,759 --> 01:27:12,888
(The cameraman in charge of Yunho today)

2621
01:27:12,889 --> 01:27:14,458
I know it will be tough,

2622
01:27:14,459 --> 01:27:16,499
but I want to finish it off with the members.

2623
01:27:16,999 --> 01:27:18,298
(We've never had a guest like him before.)

2624
01:27:18,299 --> 01:27:19,899
We've never had a guest like him before.

2625
01:27:20,069 --> 01:27:21,338
(Tell us how you feel before going home.)

2626
01:27:21,339 --> 01:27:23,398
Thanks to Seon Ho,

2627
01:27:23,399 --> 01:27:25,208
I got to join 2 Days 1 Night,

2628
01:27:25,209 --> 01:27:28,538
