- No, we are just grateful.
- Please call me anytime.

2630
01:27:30,879 --> 01:27:32,908
- And I'll come running right away.
- Thank you.

2631
01:27:32,909 --> 01:27:34,178
Thank you so much.

2632
01:27:34,179 --> 01:27:36,018
Jae Jun, you're leaving now.

2633
01:27:36,019 --> 01:27:37,418
Please clap the slate before you go.

2634
01:27:37,419 --> 01:27:38,588
- Okay.
- All right.

2635
01:27:38,589 --> 01:27:39,989
One, two, three.

2636
01:27:42,619 --> 01:27:43,619
