2640
01:27:54,699 --> 01:27:56,298
(Mount Ami: The highest mountain in Dangjin)

2641
01:27:56,299 --> 01:27:58,038
(The name is originated from the fact that...)

2642
01:27:58,039 --> 01:27:59,845
