- Right.

2674
01:29:07,779 --> 01:29:09,879
They often compare life to hiking.

2675
01:29:10,139 --> 01:29:11,449
- Hiking?
- Yes.

2676
01:29:11,879 --> 01:29:13,379
- Right.
- What do they say?

2677
01:29:13,879 --> 01:29:16,149
Something suddenly came to mind.

2678
01:29:16,419 --> 01:29:18,219
If you climb a mountain,

2679
01:29:18,919 --> 01:29:21,389
