2681
01:29:24,459 --> 01:29:25,858
You must come down once.

2682
01:29:25,859 --> 01:29:27,129
- To climb again?
- Yes.

2683
01:29:28,859 --> 01:29:30,158
Let's push on.

2684
01:29:30,159 --> 01:29:32,528
- Yes. We must go.
- We must go.

2685
01:29:32,529 --> 01:29:34,899
(Passionate Yunho gives the others strength.)

2686
01:29:35,069 --> 01:29:36,299
- Oh, gosh.
- Oh, dear.

2687
01:29:36,899 --> 01:29:38,569
