- A stairway to the sky.

2688
01:29:39,209 --> 01:29:40,638
This will take us way up.

2689
01:29:40,639 --> 01:29:42,108
Straight to the sky.

2690
01:29:42,109 --> 01:29:43,208
(The end is out of sight.)

2691
01:29:43,209 --> 01:29:45,479
These stairs end at the peak.

2692
01:29:46,849 --> 01:29:48,349
I think we're almost there.

2693
01:29:48,419 --> 01:29:50,149
Yes. We're almost there.

2694
01:29:50,379 --> 01:29:51,849
- I see the peak.
- We're there.

2695
01:29:52,249 --> 01:29:53,249
I see it.

2696
01:29:53,689 --> 01:29:55,058
- Stay strong.
- We're almost there!

2697
01:29:55,059 --> 01:29:56,289
We're almost there.

2698
01:29:56,919 --> 01:29:57,988
We're nearly there.

2699
01:29:57,989 --> 01:29:59,358
(The stairway to the sky...)

2700
01:29:59,359 --> 01:30:02,329
(keeps on going.)

2701
01:30:03,399 --> 01:30:07,029
(All we can hear is their pants.)

2702
01:30:07,169 --> 01:30:09,099
I turned around and we came pretty far.

2703
01:30:10,299 --> 01:30:11,468
(At last, )

2704
01:30:11,469 --> 01:30:12,668
These steps are narrow.

2705
01:30:12,669 --> 01:30:14,979
