2706
01:30:15,239 --> 01:30:16,639
I think we're almost there.

2707
01:30:16,979 --> 01:30:18,409
I'm just looking at the ground.

2708
01:30:18,809 --> 01:30:20,449
Let's see. Okay.

2709
01:30:21,849 --> 01:30:24,148
