Goodness. Those stairs...

2715
01:30:36,199 --> 01:30:37,728
(Feeling lost)

2716
01:30:37,729 --> 01:30:39,069
- There are about 70.
- Yes.

2717
01:30:39,269 --> 01:30:40,639
I know why this is Mount Ami.

2718
01:30:41,169 --> 01:30:42,969
