2731
01:31:18,639 --> 01:31:20,209
- Yes, a greeting.
- Jong Min.

2732
01:31:20,539 --> 01:31:21,779
Stand behind me.

2733
01:31:22,209 --> 01:31:23,708
- Why?
- I want to greet you too.

2734
01:31:23,709 --> 01:31:26,779
(Go to the far back.)

2735
01:31:27,079 --> 01:31:29,849
That fart... Right in my face.

2736
01:31:30,479 --> 01:31:32,019
I didn't know you were so close.

2737
01:31:37,259 --> 01:31:38,589
- Yunho.
- Yes?

2738
01:31:38,789 --> 01:31:40,799
- I want to give up.
- No, Se Yoon.

2739
01:31:41,329 --> 01:31:43,159
The way back from here...

2740
01:31:43,859 --> 01:31:46,068
is further than what's left.

2741
01:31:46,069 --> 01:31:47,939
Thanks, Yunho.

2742
01:31:48,199 --> 01:31:49,898
Let's keep going.

2743
01:31:49,899 --> 01:31:51,368
(Yunho's words keep him going.)

2744
01:31:51,369 --> 01:31:52,709
You can make it.

2745
01:31:53,939 --> 01:31:55,409
Great. Let's do this.

2746
01:31:55,709 --> 01:31:57,039
We're almost there.

2747
01:31:59,779 --> 01:32:01,778
Hey. We made it.

2748
01:32:01,779 --> 01:32:04,449
(After much hard work, they reach the peak!)

2749
01:32:05,449 --> 01:32:07,388
(Now they're at the top, )

2750
01:32:07,389 --> 01:32:08,788
This is amazing.

2751
01:32:08,789 --> 01:32:10,829
(they take in the amazing view.)

2752
01:32:10,959 --> 01:32:12,659
- The peak of Mount Ami.
- Mount Ami.

2753
01:32:12,829 --> 01:32:14,198
Let's take a photo here.

2754
01:32:14,199 --> 01:32:15,899
- Mount Ami.
- Let's take a photo.

2755
01:32:16,459 --> 01:32:18,629
One, two, three.

2756
01:32:19,769 --> 01:32:22,469
(They scaled Mount Ami.)

2757
01:32:22,769 --> 01:32:25,109
The Dangjin Tour of Passion with U-Know Yunho!

2758
01:32:25,739 --> 01:32:27,409
With great energy from Mount Ami.

2759
01:32:27,809 --> 01:32:29,008
Who are we?

2760
01:32:29,009 --> 01:32:30,038
(He succeeded this time.)

2761
01:32:30,039 --> 01:32:32,478
- 2 Days 1 Night.
- 1 Night.

2762
01:32:32,479 --> 01:32:34,479
- Take off!
- Take off!

2763
01:32:36,749 --> 01:32:40,219
(Visit Dangjin where there's lots to do.)

2764
01:32:40,419 --> 01:32:42,259
(Next episode)

2765
01:32:42,659 --> 01:32:45,489
(To enjoy a lovely spring outing...)

2766
01:32:46,089 --> 01:32:49,459
(you need enough money.)

2767
01:32:49,829 --> 01:32:51,929
(The members want to spend freely, )

2768
01:32:52,499 --> 01:32:55,599
(so they fight for an allowance.)

2769
01:32:56,039 --> 01:32:58,039
(The consecutive successes...)

2770
01:32:58,339 --> 01:33:01,039
(make them get their hopes up.)

2771
01:33:01,609 --> 01:33:03,378
(At this rate...)

2772
01:33:03,379 --> 01:33:05,179
(will we end up rich?)

2773
01:33:05,549 --> 01:33:08,579
(As if.)

2774
01:33:09,079 --> 01:33:11,748
(Was it ever easy...)

2775
01:33:11,749 --> 01:33:13,649
(to make a living?)

2776
01:33:13,689 --> 01:33:14,719
What are you doing?

2777
01:33:14,889 --> 01:33:18,529
(Distrust spreads)

2778
01:33:18,989 --> 01:33:23,029
(The allowance becomes harder to come by.)

2779
01:33:23,599 --> 01:33:27,999
(Will they be able to keep their allowance?)

2780
01:33:28,069 --> 01:33:30,599
(See you next week.)
